Task
Number of numbers in an array
Write a function countNumbers that takes an array arr as an argument and returns the number of elements of type "number".
Example:
• the countNumbers function ([0, 4.1, 'Alice', true, 1, false, 'hohoho']) must return 3.
• the countNumbers ([]) function must return 0.
• the countNumbers (['a', 'b']) function must return 0.

Solution
function countNumbers (arr) {
let count = 0;
for (let i = 0; i <arr.length; i ++) {
  if (typeof arr [i] === 'number')
  count ++;
  }
  return count;
}
